# Retro 90s Style Guide

## Color Palette

Custom color palette (use inline styles or CSS variables):

- **Light Orange**: `#FBD0A6` - Soft text, backgrounds
- **Pumpkin**: `#F37022` - Highlights, call-to-actions
- **Cornell Red**: `#B11016` - Strong accents, headers
- **Keppel**: `#2ABA9E` - Links, interactive elements
- **Cerulean**: `#007096` - Primary text, structure
- **Dark Background**: `#001a1a` - Base background

## Typography

```html
<!-- Headlines: Bold, Impact font -->
<h1 class="font-impact text-4xl" style="color: #F37022;">Welcome!</h1>

<!-- Body text: Courier or Arial -->
<p class="font-courier text-lg" style="color: #FBD0A6;">Content here...</p>

<!-- Pixel font for special elements -->
<p class="font-pixel" style="color: #2ABA9E;">Retro text</p>
```

