## Background Patterns

Use repeating patterns or starfield backgrounds:

```html
<body class="bg-black bg-[url('./assets/images/stars.gif')] bg-repeat">
```

## Animated Elements

- jQuery effects: `.fadeIn()`, `.slideDown()`, `.animate()`
- CSS animations for blinking text (use sparingly)
- Cursor sparkle trail
- Rainbow text animations using color palette

## Layout Tips

- Center content with max-width: `<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">`
- Use borders generously with palette colors: `border-4 border-double` with `border-color: #2ABA9E`
- Use `.retro-table` class for consistent styling
- Starfield background with animated colored stars
